text: Coen Stolk (born 26 June 1997) is a Dutch professional basketball player for Feyenoord Basketball of the Dutch Basketball League (DBL). ==Career== Stolk formerly played for Landstede Zwolle where he started his career before signing with Rotterdam Basketbal in 2015. Stolk averaged 6.7 points and 3.1 rebounds per game during the 2019-20 season.
